 get some confused readers wondering why they can=E2=80=99t get it
for Christmas! I got an early copy, too, and it=E2=80=99s excellent. But fo=
r any readers looking for a Christmas read, I=E2=80=99d recommend Kingdom o=
n Fire by Scott Howard-Cooper, about Kareem=E2=80=99s time at UCLA, or The =
Racket by Conor Niland, about life on the pro tennis circuit for those outs=
ide the top 100. Both are incredible books any sports fan will enjoy.=E2=80=
=9D =E2=80=94A professional book reviewer

On New York neighborhoods: =E2=80=9CLove the newsletter, but Puck=E2=80=99s=
 headquarters is right near the Stock Exchange. You=E2=80=99re in FiDi (whi=
ch is fine!) not =E2=80=98South Tribeca,=E2=80=99 as you often write.=E2=80=
=9D =E2=80=94Magellan, himself

On my reporting on Netflix=E2=80=99s internal Tyson-Paul numbers: =E2=80=9C=
I like that you=E2=80=99re free to use the word bullshit when you write now=
=2E Feels more authentic.=E2=80=9D =E2=80=94A=
 straight-talking sports media P=
=2ER. executive

